<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">何草不黄</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsond1e4396ece28">
<p>何草不黄？何日不行？何人不将？经营四方。</p>
<p>何草不玄？何人不矜？哀我征夫，独为匪民。</p>
<p>匪兕匪虎，率彼旷野。哀我征夫，朝夕不暇。</p>
<p>有芃者狐，率彼幽草。有栈之车，行彼周道。</p>
</div>
</div>
